title: Once Upon A December - Good Omens
author: Jala Draws
comment:
"C- Crowley?" (Y-you're real? I wasn't imagining you? ;n; )
"A... Angel?" (Y-you're alive?! ;o; )

I love this. I actually cried. My heart hurts 💔
This song is my childhood and I love AUs where Azira turns human and forgets Crowley. The angst. Also this was poignant and beautiful
"PAINTED WINGS" THAT WAS SUCH A GOOD WAY TO DO THAT SISHNSSHVSKSHSKSISVSIS

Omg when Crowley is protecting all the little ones with his wings

My heart

I love this so much. I can't believe that Aziraphale was turned human and had his memories wiped. The painted wings broke my heart and I would love to write something for this! I doubt I'd get around to it soon because I'm going to be really busy for quite a while but this deserves a story. With your permission I'd like to ask someone I know if they would like to write a story to this. Again loved this, it was absolutely beautiful! Thank you!
